{"tid":289562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屋主拿大砍刀開無雙　力抗持槍歹徒一打三","createTime":"2017-06-19T06:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T09:40:07.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89133879bf159d0625affbb849ce34d88ffd184f","tid":289562,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T06:17:06.000Z","msg":"叔叔有練過！美國佛羅里達州日前有戶人家被歹徒持槍搶劫，情急之下的屋主為了保護自己與家人，隨手抓起了一把大砍刀反擊，最後竟成功擊退3名歹徒，整個過程都被監視錄影器錄了下來，網友看完都不禁大讚屋主真是「狠角色」！<br />\n<br />\n根據《每日郵報》報導，美國警方已成功逮捕持槍搶劫的3名搶匪，還有負責在外面把風的2名同夥，並在現場找到作案用的槍枝，包括一把散彈槍。<br />\n<br />\n雖然屋主的行為很勇敢，不過警方還是要提醒民眾，用大砍刀對抗散彈槍是十分不智的。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170618/1142889/%E5%B1%8B%E4%B8%BB%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E7%A0%8D%E5%88%80%E9%96%8B%E7%84%A1%E9%9B%99%E3%80%80%E5%8A%9B%E6%8A%97%E6%8C%81%E6%A7%8D%E6%AD%B9%E5%BE%92%E4%B8%80%E6%89%93%E4%B8%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170618%2F1142889%2F%25E5%25B1%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25A0%258D%25E5%2588%2580%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%259B%2599%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%258A%2597%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%25AD%25B9%25E5%25BE%2592%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2589%2593%25E4%25B8%2589&d=iZ1a9SmCMlNlwUAqsoevFDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=605ea1e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170618/1142889/%E5%B1%8B%E4%B8%BB%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E7%A0%8D%E5%88%80%E9%96%8B%E7%84%A1%E9%9B%99%E3%80%80%E5%8A%9B%E6%8A%97%E6%8C%81%E6%A7%8D%E6%AD%B9%E5%BE%92%E4%B8%80%E6%89%93%E4%B8%89</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5353277c644565616d995b6961bdf74b66a594","tid":289562,"uid":71960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T06:26:50.000Z","msg":"豬肉刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor